des:
Welcome to pregnancy music. This skill allows you to play pregnancy music, which is soothing classical music for babies brain development or even for yourself to a deep and relaxing sleep. Just say 'open pregnancy music' to play this skill. You can say 'stop' anytime during the playback to stop.

If you love this skill, please let us know by giving us your rating!
